text.tspan: Qi-1: heat flow rate from each segment of the borehole to ground, at timi-1
Ti-1: wall temperatures of each borehole segment, at timi-1
timi-1: end time of last TOUGH simulation
"INFILE": file that includes thermal properties of ground and borehole, start/stop time and step size
"INCON": initial temperatures (borehole, ground) of the simulation domain, at timi-1
"GENER": file that includes heat flow rate from borehole to ground
"SAVE": TOUGH result file at time timi
Ti: wall temperatures of each borehole segment, at timi
Qi: heat flow rate from each segment
of the borehole to ground, at timi-1
